"{\"uid\": \"skynews.com.au-australia-news-sport-james-magnussen-blasts-paris-2024-olympic-village-conditions-claims-unsettled-athletes-will-miss-out-on-medals-news-story-a677436ce30544e54a2ea9ee92a84233\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 Olympic Village has faced a record number of complaints over uncomfortable beds and vegan meals and could cost athletes the chance at glory, according to former world champion James Magnussen.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999856072465, \"rank\": 1.4392665627953675e-08, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 30, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 2.860572821823436e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 191, \"end\": 206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Magnussen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Magnussen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Magnussen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Magnussen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former Australian swimmer James Magnussen has hit out at Paris organisers over the poor living conditions in the Olympic Village, claiming the games have received a record number of complaints from athletes.\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9998604966134736, \"rank\": 0.0001006152820410849, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 235, \"end\": 250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Magnussen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Magnussen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Magnussen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Magnussen\"}, {\"begin\": 266, \"end\": 271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999970273166, \"rank\": 2.972683763687516e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 322, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 2.860572821823436e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 33-year-old claimed on the Matty & The Missile podcast the poor sleeping conditions, notably the cardboard beds, and inadequate dietary provisions could cost athletes their chance at a medal.\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Magnussen told Fox League host Matty Johns from Paris: \\\"There will be many athletes across the two weeks of competition who miss out on a medal\\u2026 because they are unsettled by this new environment.\\\"\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 630, \"end\": 640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fox League\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_League\"}, {\"begin\": 646, \"end\": 657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Johns\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matty Johns\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Johns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Johns\"}, {\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999970273166, \"rank\": 2.972683763687516e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have not seen this at an Olympic games before.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have not had this amount of complaints about a village in Olympics history.\\\"\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The discontent has been so severe the American tennis team has left the Olympic Village for a nearby hotel.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 1053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999838933584864, \"rank\": 1.1757488349155074e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1018, \"end\": 1033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 2.860572821823436e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"US tennis star Coco Gauff highlighted the cramped conditions on social media with the caption \\\"10 girls, two bathrooms\\\".\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9967955402818427, \"rank\": 0.0022383211734745647, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1070, \"end\": 1080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian water polo athlete Tilly Kearns has also voiced her frustration, calling the beds \\\"rock hard\\\".\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1213, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Kearns\", \"score\": 0.9999943677816548, \"rank\": 5.623456654251326e-06, \"text\": \"Kearns\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Kearns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Kearns\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Magnussen and Johns have slammed the bed frames, reportedly made from styrofoam and cardboard as \\\"ridiculous\\\".\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Modern-day athletes, sometimes they can be pampered, but I look at this and it is ridiculous,\\\" Johns said.\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People have trained so hard for four years.\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They turn up here and they are sleeping on cardboard beds?\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just ridiculous.\\\"\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another major point of contention has been the food offering as Magnussen reported the village ran out of meat on the first day.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I joked last night about the amount of vegan options in the village, that they are running out of meat,\\\" Magnussen said.\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, an Australian heavyweight boxer has come out.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1896, \"end\": 1906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9998604966134736, \"rank\": 0.0001006152820410849, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wanted lamb chops - (but there is a) maximum two chops per person.\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The guy is 6'6\\\", 110(kg) at best.\\\"\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Johns joked: \\\"He's come here as a heavyweight, he will go home as a middleweight.\\\"\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The apparent lack of adequate living conditions has taken a toll on athlete performance, according to Magnussen.\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2241, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We saw again tonight great results in the pool but as far as times goes, they are well off those world (record) marks,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think it's a slow pool.\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's sleeping on cardboard beds\\u2026 At the end of the day, it's about who can overcome these setbacks, who can put these distractions aside.\\\"\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To join the conversation, pleaselog in.Do not have an account?Register  Join the conversation, you are commenting asLogout  Our Apps\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2680, \"entities\": []}]}"